129
00:09:51,860 --> 00:09:57,020
What a city! Frankfurt has so many great old movie theaters.

130
00:09:57,660 --> 00:09:59,800
That movie was on TV just last week.

131
00:10:00,420 --> 00:10:02,380
That one really brings me to tears.

132
00:10:03,280 --> 00:10:05,400
