156
00:11:01,720 --> 00:11:03,680
We've missed some, but they'll still let us in.

157
00:11:04,220 --> 00:11:08,040
Oh, it's just... well, I...

158
00:11:08,040 --> 00:11:12,120
Some other time. It is kind of late, and you're still eating.

159
00:11:12,580 --> 00:11:13,060
Sorry.

160
