163
00:11:21,900 --> 00:11:22,480
[children laughing]

164
00:11:25,780 --> 00:11:27,000
Well, I'm back.

165
00:11:27,880 --> 00:11:30,020
Great! So, how was your break?

166
00:11:30,260 --> 00:11:32,400
Oh, can I scrub that for you?

167
00:11:32,780 --> 00:11:34,500
