00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:58,220
Mm-hmm.

201
00:14:58,680 --> 00:15:01,420
That just means you haven't learned how to make it proper.

202
00:15:03,420 --> 00:15:05,140
This cooking's tough stuff.

203
