208
00:15:54,800 --> 00:15:55,620
- That's true.

209
00:15:56,300 --> 00:15:58,780
When I was younger, I always wanted to watch movies,

210
00:15:58,900 --> 00:16:00,700
but with work, I never had the time to.

211
00:16:02,020 --> 00:16:04,720
Back then, I ate a lot of fabulous meals,

212
00:16:04,960 --> 00:16:05,980
but to be really honest,

213
00:16:06,080 --> 00:16:08,740
