That was it."

225
00:17:01,800 --> 00:17:05,120
"So how did you find out about me and what I did?"

226
00:17:05,120 --> 00:17:07,480
"From one of my professors at law school.

227
00:17:07,480 --> 00:17:13,180
He had done research on you and all the cases you were involved in the Ristorante Nino case

