suppose you want to know how many people I killed.

236
00:18:07,620 --> 00:18:10,380
To be honest with you, I can't even remember.

237
00:18:10,380 --> 00:18:17,920
I was never a good kid, and before I knew what was what I was in way over my head.

238
00:18:19,080 --> 00:18:22,120
Robbery, blackmail, if you can name it, then I did it.

239
00:18:22,560 --> 00:18:25,000
And eventually I became a hitman.

240
00:18:26,460 --> 00:18:29,320
I rewarded myself by eating very well.

241
00:18:38,500 --> 00:18:41,100
I never had any feelings about it.

242
00:18:41,380 --> 00:18:42,500
